&lt;p&gt;This is a full time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll do at Figma:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paint the vision of the Figma Platform and guide customers in realizing the value through product demonstrations and presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Sales team by addressing Figma platform questions and showcasing how Figma accelerates digital product delivery to prospective customers (pre-sales) and existing customers (post-sales)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the customer IT and Security relationship during the deal cycle by addressing security questionnaires, RFIs, RFPs, identity and enterprise questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Support to identify opportunities for enhancing account security through new product features and help influence the product roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strengthen Figma&#39;s security reputation by understanding customer concerns about data access and working with product and legal teams to resolve findings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and scale technical sales efforts, facilitating conversations and connections between our customers, sales and product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create thoughtful content to delight customers and internal partners surrounding the Figma platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with amazing Figmates to hone your craft and execute daily. We are looking for fantastic life-long learners who can operate with autonomy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;We&#39;d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years professional experience including familiarity with positioning software in a presales capacity and implementing technology post-sales.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to adapt to new technologies, learn quickly, and problem solve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills within a variety of audiences and a knack for delivering compelling presentations and product demonstrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with the enterprise SaaS ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize competing demands from customers and balance their needs against those of the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;While not required, it’s an added plus if you also have:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with developer workflows and frontend frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
