&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Product Manager to join our Creation Engine pillar, the foundational teams that power Figma&#39;s canvas, rendering, performance, and extensions across all products. This role sits at the intersection of cutting-edge web technology, creative tools, and AI innovation, building the foundation that enables millions of designers and developers to create and collaborate in ways that weren&#39;t possible before. You&#39;ll lead two critical teams, SceneGraph &amp;amp; Sync and Fullscreen Platform, driving the core data model, real-time collaboration infrastructure, and platform foundations that power all Figma products across web, desktop, and mobile.&lt;/p&gt;
