&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of sales experience (preferably within SaaS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of management experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of our technical and competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in a constantly changing and evolving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional coaching, writing, discovery and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excitement for increasing customer happiness and developing lasting customer relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of leading successful and consistent sales team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
